                                as:<br>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Ad identifiers and other information collected from your device. Information about how you interact with our App and Services;</li>
                                    <li>Your age, country and region, and gender; and</li>
                                    <li>Other demographic and interests based information that we might acquire from our third party marketing partners 
                                    or other third parties who have obtained your consent or have another legal right to share that information with 
